snippet.textDisplay: JENNA MARBLES IVE BEEN WANTING TO WRITE THID COMMENT FOREVER I LITERALLY WISH NOTHING BUT FOR YOU TO SEE IT AND KNOW that I love chihuahuas. My grandmother has a ‘teacup’ chihuahua that is 14 years old. He’s getting very old, very weak, he’s had a lot of health issues regarding mainly his legs and walking. Now it’s his heart and cataracts. Just a part of getting old. His name is Chico and much like Marbles he only likes very little people such as my grandmother, grandfather, and me. Ive has him my whole life and my grandmother even joked that he would be my wedding gift. When I was maybe 7 or 8, I made him a mailbox out of cardboard, decorated it and everything and sent him love letters. I love him so much and would give everything to keep him going but I know deep down his time is coming even tho it’s complete denial. I just want you to know I love you and all your dogs and especially marbles. I’ve been watching you since about 2013 (I’m 20 now) and I just love you and everything you are. Thank you Marbles for creating Jenna marbles
